SIMPLE: streaming
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Streaming
<hw>Stream"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Sending forth streams.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Streaming</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Streaming
<hw>Stream"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act or operation
of that which streams; the act of that which sends forth, or which runs
in, streams.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Mining)</fld> <def>The reduction of stream tin;
also, the search for stream tin.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Biol.)</fld> <def>the rapid flow of cytoplasm
within a cell; -- called also <altname>protoplasmic
streaming</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Streamless</ent>⟦br⟧
